summary: I am a graduate of the Medical University of Poznan. In my work, I use knowledge in the field of medicine and business. In my opinion, medical services are closely related to business tools. I try to develop in medicine as well as learn new marketing techniques. I'm fascinated by the new achievements of telemedicine. My greatest passion is self-development. I have extensive experience working with clients, staff training, recruitment, construction of new marketing tools for companies in the branch of medicine, insurance, and the process of liquidation of personal injury. My passion is working with people and for people.
